author: Kevin Goddard
title: Young Dolph - That's How I Feel Feat. Gucci Mane
text:
0 NOT FEELING IT 0 MAKE IT STOP Young Dolph links up with Gucci Mane for the new single "That's How I Feel," off his upcoming album "Bulletproof." As if last month’s Gelato mixtape wasn’t enough for fans, Young Dolph just announced that he’s planning on releasing a new album in a few weeks called Bulletproof . Already available for preorder on iTunes , those of you who take advantage of the early purchase will receive this new song for free as an instant download called “That’s How It Feels” featuring Gucci Mane . Take a listen to the Drumma Boy -produced street banger & let us know what you think. Bulletproof arrives 4/1. GO PRE-ORDER NOW! And u get da first single "That's How I Feel" ft @gucci1017 #BulletProof pic.twitter.com/Qefu2YRov6 — its DOLP ! (@YoungDolph) March 11, 2017 
Quotable Lyrics: 
Shipping money by the mail, I just came back with the bills Now Im dancing in the truck thats how I feel Im in a coupe cost half a mill I just redid my Chevelle, got 2 Maybachs in both thats just how I feel I got two bitches at the ‘tel, hope that they don't kiss & tell Im way too much for just one bitch thats just how I feel 
- Guwop
